column5: After getting knocked around by the wind last week in our inflatable, i had hopes for this weekends winds to be fair, got there and guess what winds were gusting hard, how can those weather people allow themselves to be called Meteorologists? Well you know weather does change quickly and depends on many factors, so its alright if they can get 1 out of 10 predictions right! stats provided by urbanangler.  Anyway here is a nice perch and sunfish, can anyone geuss the length of the perch? let it be a game if u wish, no prizes though
Nice report and pics  I'll gestimate it at 11.5"  Leechman
I guesstimate the Perch at 12"... nice Jumbo!!!  ... did you have a sunburn today?
Nice perch UA. Geez i think you should stop reading GCD's reports and imitating his fish poses
honestly i dont think ive read 2 of his reports, lol
